WEBVTT

00:02.712 --> 00:05.882
[ Electronic hum ]

00:10.787 --> 00:12.789
Finn: Squish.

00:12.822 --> 00:15.925
Photosynthesize!

00:15.958 --> 00:18.895
Photosynthesize!

00:18.928 --> 00:21.130
Photo--
You grabbing a snack, Fern?

00:21.163 --> 00:22.632
Yeah.

00:22.665 --> 00:25.402
Water and light combine
so I can make my own food.

00:25.435 --> 00:27.404
In case
I don't catch anything.

00:27.437 --> 00:30.239
Come on, man.
Don't be so dow --
[ Reel clicks, squeaks ]

00:30.273 --> 00:31.608
[ Gasps ]
Hey, I got something!

00:31.641 --> 00:34.611
[ Reel clicking ]
Hey, I got something, too!

00:38.415 --> 00:39.749
Nice.

00:39.782 --> 00:41.951
[ Grunts ]

00:41.984 --> 00:43.586
[ Growling ]

00:43.620 --> 00:45.422
Oh, no!
Oh, no! Oh, no!

00:46.523 --> 00:47.857
[ Sighs ]

00:50.593 --> 00:52.061
Pretty weird fish, huh?

00:52.094 --> 00:55.832
That's me --
the dude who dinks it up,

00:55.865 --> 00:58.535
just like I dinked it up
when you left Ooo.

00:58.568 --> 01:00.670
I was supposed
to protect it.

01:00.703 --> 01:03.005
Instead,
it went all crazy.

01:03.039 --> 01:04.006
I didn't even help.

01:04.040 --> 01:05.842
I just covered myself
in root beer

01:05.875 --> 01:07.810
and danced around
like a dummy.

01:07.844 --> 01:12.349
I can't do anything right!

01:12.382 --> 01:14.351
Hey, stop it.

01:14.384 --> 01:15.985
You need a squoze?

01:16.018 --> 01:17.354
Yes.

01:17.387 --> 01:19.522
[ Grunts ]

01:19.556 --> 01:20.990
I feel better.

01:21.023 --> 01:24.327
Sometimes being a good dude
ain't about not dinking it.

01:24.361 --> 01:25.562
Learn from your dinks.

01:25.595 --> 01:28.531
Like, you know my first battle
with a giant?

01:28.565 --> 01:30.032
I never told anybody this,
but --

01:30.066 --> 01:31.701
You boom-boomed
in your shorts.

01:31.734 --> 01:34.203
I know.
I have your memories.

01:34.236 --> 01:36.238
Yeah, I boom-boomed.

01:36.272 --> 01:39.542
The point is I learned from it,
and now I'm Finn.

01:39.576 --> 01:41.778
You got to learn
how to be Fern.

01:41.811 --> 01:44.280
[ Stomping, rumbling ]

01:44.313 --> 01:45.415
Both: What's that sound?

01:45.448 --> 01:47.617
Oh, I bet
it's a monster.

01:47.650 --> 01:49.419
Let's fight this dude
Fern's way.

01:49.452 --> 01:51.788
Yeah.
Fern's way.

01:51.821 --> 01:53.623
[ Stomping, rumbling continue ]

01:53.656 --> 01:55.692
Aaaaah!

01:55.725 --> 01:58.160
Both: Sweet P?
Waaaah!

01:58.194 --> 02:00.062
Both: Whoa!

02:01.330 --> 02:03.299
Sweet P:
Aaaaaaaaaaaah!
Both: [ Gasp ]

02:03.332 --> 02:09.105
Waaaaaaaaaaaaaah!

02:09.138 --> 02:11.474
Okay, Fern, what do you think
we should do next?

02:11.508 --> 02:13.643
Mm, sever his tendons?

02:13.676 --> 02:15.044
[ Winces ]

02:15.077 --> 02:18.114
Before you say no,
it would stop him from running.

02:18.147 --> 02:21.150
We're gonna handle this
librarian style.

02:21.183 --> 02:22.452
[ Crying ]

02:22.485 --> 02:24.320
[ Whispering ] Shh.

02:24.353 --> 02:26.789
Librarian.
Kiss.

02:26.823 --> 02:30.393
You can renew the book
and bring it back next week.

02:30.427 --> 02:31.994
Library style.

02:32.028 --> 02:35.865
Squ-o-o-oze.

02:35.898 --> 02:37.066
Ooh.

02:38.501 --> 02:41.203
Mm.
Great thinking, Fern.

02:41.237 --> 02:44.040
I just copied you.
Is that thinking?

02:44.073 --> 02:47.610
What up, buttercup?
Why you run, pork bun?

02:47.644 --> 02:49.479
The monster!

02:49.512 --> 02:51.147
Was it LSP?

02:52.181 --> 02:56.653
The monster that whispers me
bad thoughts.

02:57.820 --> 03:01.791
[ Indistinct whispering ]

03:03.693 --> 03:05.061
[ Whispering stops ]

03:05.094 --> 03:07.930
Sweet P: Mommy and Daddy came
to save me,

03:07.964 --> 03:11.300
but they said
I was imagining things,

03:11.333 --> 03:13.202
which was true.

03:16.038 --> 03:19.075
[ Indistinct whispering ]

03:19.108 --> 03:22.144
Sweet P: But last night,
I really did see it.

03:23.713 --> 03:26.015
[ Screams ]

03:26.048 --> 03:28.785
And I've been running
and running since then.

03:28.818 --> 03:31.120
Aww, Sweet P.

03:31.153 --> 03:33.823
It sounds like you might
just be having bad dreams.

03:33.856 --> 03:37.627
No, I only have
one dream anymore.

03:37.660 --> 03:40.329
[ Indistinct whispering ]

03:40.362 --> 03:42.965
Uhh...
Uhh...

03:42.999 --> 03:46.869
But the whisper monster is
even scarier,

03:46.903 --> 03:50.707
saying stuff like,
"Sweet P, you're bad.

03:50.740 --> 03:54.076
You always have been bad."

03:54.110 --> 03:56.412
I don't want to be bad.

03:56.445 --> 03:58.380
[ Crying ]

03:58.414 --> 04:00.917
Oh, you're not bad.
You're super good.

04:00.950 --> 04:02.184
Now, let's get you home.

04:02.218 --> 04:03.586
But it's getting late,

04:03.620 --> 04:06.689
and bogs are super dangerous
to travel in at night.

04:06.723 --> 04:10.627
Your body will be preserved
for thousands of years.

04:10.660 --> 04:14.230
No one will ever find you.

04:14.263 --> 04:16.432
[ Wailing ]
Fern!

04:17.466 --> 04:20.402
Okay, okay, we'll see you
in the morning, Tree Trunks.

04:20.436 --> 04:23.606
[ Telephone beeps ]
All right, bedtime,
Sweet P.

04:24.974 --> 04:27.409
You want me
to knock him out?

04:27.443 --> 04:31.247
Er, not this time.
How about a bedtime story?

04:31.280 --> 04:32.381
Yes, please.

04:32.414 --> 04:36.318
Once there was
a kingdom of spaghetti.

04:36.352 --> 04:37.787
Mmm.

04:37.820 --> 04:39.421
[ Insects chirping ]

04:39.455 --> 04:42.124
[ Snoring ]

04:42.158 --> 04:44.694
[ Whispering ]
Punch, punch.

04:44.727 --> 04:46.195
Kiss, kiss.

04:46.228 --> 04:50.032
The Lich:
Listen to your bones.

04:51.433 --> 04:52.869
Fern.

04:52.902 --> 04:54.671
[ Teeth clicking ]

04:54.704 --> 04:55.872
Fern!

04:55.905 --> 04:57.740
[ Gasps ]

04:57.774 --> 04:59.842
Hey. What's up?

04:59.876 --> 05:01.210
I heard something.

05:01.243 --> 05:03.379
Can you see what it is
with your tree senses?

05:03.412 --> 05:06.282
I don't have those.
[ Rustle ]

05:11.053 --> 05:13.122
[ Footsteps ]

05:13.856 --> 05:15.758
Uh, can I help you?

05:15.792 --> 05:17.226
Oh, sorry.

05:17.259 --> 05:18.895
We heard you scuttling
around and thought --

05:18.928 --> 05:20.196
What?

05:20.229 --> 05:21.998
You didn't hear me
"scuttling around."

05:22.031 --> 05:23.733
Foxes are silent hunters.

05:23.766 --> 05:26.535
I mean, geez, do you know
how rude that is?

05:26.569 --> 05:29.772
[Groans] Gonna be brooding
about this all week.

05:29.806 --> 05:30.907
Sorry, man.

05:30.940 --> 05:32.709
[ Indistinct whispering ]
Look.

05:32.742 --> 05:34.443
[ Whispering continues ]

05:34.476 --> 05:36.445
Aah!
Get off him!

05:36.478 --> 05:37.714
Lich Hand: Huh?

05:37.747 --> 05:39.415
Aah!
[ Grunts ]

05:43.052 --> 05:44.453
I got him!

05:44.486 --> 05:45.788
Oh, no.

05:45.822 --> 05:48.090
I know where I've seen
that thing before.

05:48.124 --> 05:52.061
[ Ominous tones play ]

05:57.834 --> 05:59.201
Huh?

06:00.502 --> 06:04.240
Lich Hand:
[ Laughs evilly ]

06:06.508 --> 06:09.145
BMO: Finn, Jake!
What's shaking?

06:09.178 --> 06:11.648
You will not believe
what just happened.

06:11.681 --> 06:15.952
It must've been the day that BMO
found that little sailor hat.

06:15.985 --> 06:17.053
Hold him down, Fern!

06:17.086 --> 06:19.656
That hand is
the flippin' Lich!

06:19.689 --> 06:20.823
I know.

06:20.857 --> 06:22.324
[ Chuckles evilly ]

06:22.358 --> 06:25.494
Yes, child.
I returned once more to --

06:25.527 --> 06:27.296
Bah! Bah! Bah!
Bah! Evil!

06:27.329 --> 06:29.666
You're gonna get it for messing
with our boy Sweet P.

06:29.699 --> 06:34.003
That vessel may appear harmless,
but he came from me.

06:34.036 --> 06:39.075
Once I remind him of his legacy,
The Lich shall reign once more.

06:39.108 --> 06:41.543
Isn't that right, son?
-Aah!

06:41.577 --> 06:43.179
Finn!

06:43.212 --> 06:44.981
Lich Hand:
[ Laughs evilly ]

06:45.014 --> 06:47.216
Ugh!
I dinked it again!

06:47.249 --> 06:49.752
[ Grunts ]

06:49.786 --> 06:52.288
[ Panting ]

06:52.321 --> 06:55.257
Why did Mr. Hand
call me "son"?

06:55.291 --> 06:57.593
Was that my monster daddy?

06:57.626 --> 06:59.829
Okay, delegate,
delegate --

06:59.862 --> 07:01.931
Fern, stay here
and guard Sweet P.

07:01.964 --> 07:05.501
I'm gonna try and catch up.
Don't trust me
to guard anything.

07:05.534 --> 07:06.936
I'm a total scrub-up.

07:06.969 --> 07:09.772
Dude, there's already
one Lich loose in Ooo.

07:09.806 --> 07:11.941
If Sweet Pea turns
e-v-i-l tonight,

07:11.974 --> 07:13.175
there might be a second.

07:13.209 --> 07:15.011
I need you here.

07:15.044 --> 07:17.113
You got this!

07:17.146 --> 07:18.948
You got this.

07:18.981 --> 07:21.650
[ The Lich's voice ]
Quickly, while the boy is gone,

07:21.684 --> 07:24.253
we must seek out
my well of power.

07:24.286 --> 07:25.654
Sweet P:
[ Normal voice ] No!

07:25.688 --> 07:28.424
Am I turning
into a monster?

07:28.457 --> 07:30.192
That's the working theory.

07:30.559 --> 07:35.297
Jake: I can't come
to the phone right now.

07:35.331 --> 07:38.500
I'm either hanging with Finn,
my kids, my G.F., or I'm dead.

07:38.534 --> 07:39.702
Bye!
[ Tone beeps ]

07:39.736 --> 07:41.637
Hey, man,
hit me when you get this.

07:41.670 --> 07:44.373
[ Clicks tongue ]
Dude's missing a Lich fight.

07:44.406 --> 07:46.408
Okay, Lich.

07:46.442 --> 07:48.444
Get ready to die --
again --

07:48.477 --> 07:50.612
for, like,
the fifth time.

07:53.149 --> 07:55.752
Oh, hey,
it's this awful place.

07:55.785 --> 07:57.820
[ Rustling ]

07:59.255 --> 08:01.323
Oh, you're tricky, huh?

08:11.233 --> 08:13.135
[ Indistinct whispering ]

08:13.169 --> 08:14.536
I can hear you down there!

08:14.570 --> 08:17.373
[ Whispering continues ]

08:17.406 --> 08:19.608
Speak up, man.
What?
[ Rustling ]

08:20.609 --> 08:23.312
Aah! Ooh!
Aaaaaah!

08:24.981 --> 08:26.448
The Lich:
[ Chuckles evilly ]

08:26.482 --> 08:29.418
You bested me
in many worlds, child,

08:29.451 --> 08:32.321
but I always return.

08:32.354 --> 08:33.923
[ Rock hisses ]
[ Grunts ]

08:33.956 --> 08:37.326
You're so evil, it's boring.
You're basic, man.

08:37.359 --> 08:38.627
Yes.

08:38.660 --> 08:42.164
While a mortal world doubts
and questions,

08:42.198 --> 08:43.966
I know exactly what I am.

08:44.000 --> 08:46.102
I am the ceaseless wheel,

08:46.135 --> 08:48.838
the last scholar of Golb.

08:48.871 --> 08:51.273
I am your doom.

08:51.307 --> 08:52.842
Sweet P: Skull man!
Huh?

08:54.110 --> 08:57.379
I, too, am doom.

09:02.785 --> 09:04.453
Hey, what's going on
up there?

09:04.486 --> 09:06.355
[ Laughs evilly ]

09:06.388 --> 09:09.792
Child, you have failed.
The vessel has turned.

09:09.826 --> 09:13.930
We reign now
as twin kings of ruin.

09:13.963 --> 09:15.631
Sweet P.

09:15.664 --> 09:18.300
I'm not a king of ruin.

09:18.334 --> 09:19.468
What?

09:19.501 --> 09:21.537
I am sweet.

09:21.570 --> 09:23.639
You're just a naughty hand.

09:23.672 --> 09:25.808
Beast, obey me!

09:25.842 --> 09:27.309
Obey -- No!

09:27.343 --> 09:30.546
[ Grunting ]

09:30.579 --> 09:32.214
[ Slice ]
Eesh.

09:32.248 --> 09:33.682
[ Groans ]

09:33.715 --> 09:36.152
[ Spirits groan, scream ]

09:36.185 --> 09:37.887
Hooray!

09:37.920 --> 09:40.890
You're a natural!
But where's Fern?

09:40.923 --> 09:44.460
He wouldn't let me follow you,
so I knocked him out cold.

09:44.493 --> 09:47.363
Yeah, I met
my bio dad once, too.

09:47.396 --> 09:50.132
He wasn't evil incarnate, but
he was kind of a crummy dude.

09:50.166 --> 09:53.769
T.T. and Mr. P. love you.
That's all that matters.

09:53.802 --> 09:56.906
Fern, Sweet P saved me
and slew The Lich!

09:56.939 --> 09:59.108
That's great.

09:59.141 --> 10:01.577
Sweet P:
You're just a naughty hand.

10:01.610 --> 10:03.445
The Lich:
Beast, obey me!

10:03.479 --> 10:05.414
Obey -- no!

10:05.447 --> 10:06.983
Male voice:
End of message.

10:07.016 --> 10:08.918
To repeat this message,
press 7.

10:08.951 --> 10:10.519
What?
-To save...

10:13.789 --> 10:15.925
Fern: I don't get it.

10:15.958 --> 10:18.394
Why isn't it working out
being myself?

10:18.427 --> 10:21.397
Finn's off having fun
defeating losers.

10:21.430 --> 10:23.132
I can't even guard a baby.

10:23.165 --> 10:25.935
It doesn't matter
how hard I try.

10:25.968 --> 10:30.606
I'll always just be
in the shadow of the real Finn.

10:30.639 --> 10:34.243
Unless I could become...

10:34.276 --> 10:36.645
the only Finn.

10:36.678 --> 10:39.781
Uh, yeah, but that's
a weird thing to call me.

10:44.586 --> 10:48.524
♪ Come along with me

10:48.557 --> 10:52.895
♪ And the butterflies and bees
